6. October 2012
===============
- Released a fully functional FakeDNS server on github.


11. January 2014
================
- Added database to log requests which the DNS-server receive. It writes
  these requests into a sqlite3 file with the help of data_mapper-gem.


8. February 2015
================
- Rebuilt the Server to be more ruby like.
- Server is now using Resolv stdlib to create and handle dns messages.
- Some modifications in application.rb are done to support the new server.
- Removed less brilliant visions i had. 

9. November 2020
================
- Removed PacketFu requirements.
